title: TUESDAY 3/9 - Big paday in Big D for Dak
itunes:title: TUESDAY 3/9 - Big paday in Big D for Dak
description:
We finally know the future of Dak Prescott (0:05). The Cowboys QB landing the big pay day he's been seeking. Tag, you're it! Washington (0:32) and the Jets (0:57) using the franchise tags while the Seahawks release Carlos Dunlap (1:18). Russell Wilson's future in Seattle unknown, but Rams pass rusher Michael Brockers would not be sad to see him go (1:58)...and Maia Chaka makes NFL history 2:25)
